---

<Layout
  title="About Expat Savvy | Swiss Insurance Experts"
  canonicalURLProp="https://expat-savvy.ch/about/"
>
  <!-- Schema.org markup -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" slot="head">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "Expat Savvy",
      "description": "Expert insurance guidance for expats in Switzerland",
      "url": "https://expat-savvy.ch",
      "logo": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dphbnwjtx/image/upload/v1740080077/logoexpatsavvy_sykutm.svg",
      "foundingDate": "2017",
      "address": {
        "@type": "PostalAddress",
        "streetAddress": "Talacker 41",
        "addressLocality": "Zürich",
        "postalCode": "8001",
        "addressCountry": "CH"
      },
      "contactPoint": {
        "@type": "ContactPoint",
        "telephone": "+41763648888",
        "contactType": "customer service",
        "availableLanguage": ["English", "German", "French"]
      },
      "sameAs": [
        "https://www.linkedin.com/company/expat-savvy"
      ],
      "employee": [
        {
          "@type": "Person",
          "name": "Benjamin Amos Wagner",
          "jobTitle": "Founder & Partner, Digital Strategy",
          "sameAs": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/benjamin-amos-wagner-5a7888a5/"
        },
        {
          "@type": "Person",
          "name": "Robert Kolar",
          "jobTitle": "Partner, Senior Consultant - Education & Insurance Partnerships",
          "sameAs": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/robert-kolar-9bb889152/"
        }
      ]
    }
  </script>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div class="relative bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img 
        src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dphbnwjtx/image/upload/v1746955727/a-photograph-of-a-pair-of-weathered-hand_VtrAh5xzQTyf2G3A5waPuw_JX12TClHSTyC9fW-makmfw_jutsp1.webp"
        alt="Swiss landscape"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        width="1920"
        height="1080"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/60 to-black/40"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6">
          <span class="block">More Than Just Insurance:</span>
          <span class="block mt-2">It's About Your <span class="text-primary-500">Swiss Adventure</span></span>
        </h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Our Story Section - Redesigned as one cohesive section -->
  <div class="bg-gray-50 py-16 relative">
    <!-- Background pattern -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pattern-diagonal-noise opacity-30 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">Our Story</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg border border-primary-400/30 mb-12 relative z-10">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Hey there! I'm Benjamin, and if you're reading this, chances are you're either planning a move to Switzerland or you've recently arrived and are trying to make sense of it all. Believe me, I get it. More than you might think.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
            For years, I've lived what many call a 'digital nomad' lifestyle. I've packed my bags and landed in more new countries than I can count on both hands – each with its own unique charm, its own set of rules, and yes, its own bewildering bureaucracy. It's not always the straightforward 'expat' assignment; often it's been about diving headfirst into the unknown, figuring things out as I go. That feeling of being 'new,' where everything from the language on the street signs to the way you buy a train ticket is an adventure (and sometimes a challenge!), is something I know intimately.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-10">
            And through all these travels and transitions, one thing became crystal clear: when you're trying to build a life or even just settle in for a while, the last thing you want to be bogged down by is confusing paperwork and systems you don't understand. Especially when it comes to something as vital as your health and security.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Why Expat Savvy? Because Helping Feels Good.</h3>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
            With over 20 years of experience as an insurance consultant, I've seen the ins and outs of the industry. I've seen how complex it can be, but also how crucial the right protection is. When I started focusing more on Switzerland, a country I deeply admire for its quality of life and stunning beauty, I saw a gap. So many international folks were arriving, full of hope and excitement, only to hit a wall of confusion when it came to Swiss insurance.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
            I wanted to change that. Honestly? Because nothing gives back more than genuinely helping someone navigate a tricky situation and seeing that look of relief on their face. It's about taking that burden off your shoulders so you can actually enjoy the incredible experience of living in Switzerland.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-10">
            Expat Savvy was born from this desire: to be that down-to-earth, straightforward guide for expats and global minds. We're not about stuffy corporate talk or pushing products. We're about listening to your story, understanding your needs, and finding the simplest, clearest path to getting you properly set up and feeling secure. We're here to translate the complex into the understandable, to be your friendly advisors who've got your back.
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Approach: Human, Honest, and Here for You</h3>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">We believe in a few simple things:</p>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-10">
            {values.map(value => (
              <div class="flex items-start bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-md">
                <div class="text-primary-600 mr-3 mt-1">
                  <Fragment set:html={value.icon} />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-base font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">{value.title}</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">{value.description}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
            This isn't just a business for me, or for our team. It's a passion. It's about making a real difference for people embarking on one of life's big adventures.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-10">
            So, whether you're just starting to plan your move or you're already here and feeling a bit overwhelmed, reach out. Let's chat. Let's figure it out together. Welcome to Switzerland – we're thrilled to help you make it home.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">
            Warmly,<br>
            Benjamin Amos Wagner
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Our Values Section -->
  <div class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">Our Values</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Expertise & Experience Value -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <div class="text-primary-600 mb-4">
            <svg class="h-10 w-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Expertise & Experience</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Our team combines deep knowledge of Swiss insurance with years of experience serving expats. We understand both the technical aspects of insurance and the unique challenges faced by international residents.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Independence & Transparency Value -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <div class="text-primary-600 mb-4">
            <svg class="h-10 w-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Independence & Transparency</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            As an independent broker, we're not tied to any insurance company. This allows us to provide unbiased advice and find the best solutions for our clients, always with full transparency about costs and benefits.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Client-Centric Approach Value -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md border border-gray-100">
          <div class="text-primary-600 mb-4">
            <svg class="h-10 w-10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Client-Centric Approach</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Every client's situation is unique. We take the time to understand your specific needs and circumstances to provide personalized recommendations that truly work for you.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Team Section -->
  <div class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">Our Team</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        {teamMembers.map(member => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden h-full flex flex-col">
            <div class="p-8 flex-1 flex flex-col">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <img 
                  src={member.image} 
                  alt={member.name}
                  srcset={member.image.includes('webp') ? 
                    `${member.image.replace('/e_improve,e_sharpen/', '/c_scale,w_200,e_improve,e_sharpen/')} 200w,
                     ${member.image.replace('/e_improve,e_sharpen/', '/c_scale,w_300,e_improve,e_sharpen/')} 300w,
                     ${member.image.replace('/e_improve,e_sharpen/', '/c_scale,w_400,e_improve,e_sharpen/')} 400w` : ''}
                  sizes="(max-width: 640px) 200px, (max-width: 1024px) 300px, 400px"
                  class="h-48 w-48 rounded-full object-cover mb-4"
                  width="400"
                  height="400"
                  loading="lazy"
                  decoding="async"
                />
                <div class="text-center">
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">{member.name}</h3>
                  <p class="text-primary-600">{member.role}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 flex-grow">{member.description}</p>
              <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Areas of Expertise:</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                  {member.expertise.map(item => (
                    <li class="flex items-start text-gray-600">
                      <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-500 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                      </svg>
                      <span class="leading-relaxed">{item}</span>
                    </li>
                  ))}
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-gray-100">
                <a 
                  href={member.linkedin}
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full px-4 py-2 border border-primary-600 text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-primary-600 bg-white hover:bg-primary-600 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200"
                >
                  <svg class="h-4 w-4 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/>
                  </svg>
                  Connect with me
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      
      <!-- Supporting Team Members -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-16">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">Our Supporting Team</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          {supportTeam.map(member => (
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">{member.name}</h4>
              <p class="text-primary-600 mb-4">{member.role}</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">{member.description}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Open Positions Button -->
      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <a 
          href="/careers" 
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 shadow-md transition-colors"
        >
          View Open Positions
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Premium Partners Section -->
  <div class="bg-gray-900 py-16 text-white relative">
    <!-- Background pattern -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pattern-black-twill opacity-40 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-center mb-12">Our Partners</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        Beyond our core team, we believe in the power of collaboration. We work closely with a trusted network of freelance specialists and partner companies in various fields – from relocation services to legal advice and tax consultancy. This allows us to provide you with comprehensive support that goes beyond just insurance, ensuring you have access to the expertise you need for a smooth transition into Swiss life.
      </p>
      
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Premium Partners</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        {premiumPartners.map(partner => (
          <a 
            href={partner.url}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center transform transition-transform hover:scale-105 h-40 border border-gray-700 hover:border-primary-500/50"
          >
            <img 
              src={partner.logo} 
              alt={partner.name}
              class="h-16 object-contain mb-4"
              width="200"
              height="64"
            />
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-center text-sm">{partner.description}</p>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Interested in Partnering with Us?</h3>
