          We are always happy to connect with new partners who share our commitment to helping expats thrive in Switzerland. If you believe our services align and we can help each other get forward, we'd love to hear from you.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="mailto:hello@expat-savvy.ch?subject=Partnership Inquiry" 
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-primary-400 text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-primary-600/80 hover:bg-primary-500 transition-colors shadow-md"
        >
          Get in Touch to Discuss Partnership Opportunities
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
